longBusinessSummary: Jadason Enterprises Ltd, an investment holding company, distributes machines and materials for the printed circuit board (PCB) and semiconductor industries in China, Hong Kong, Japan, Malaysia, Singapore, Thailand, and Taiwan. It operates through Equipment and Supplies, and Manufacturing and Support Services segments. The company also provides resharpening services to the PCB industry; and sales support and procurement services, as well as drilling services to the PCB and semiconductor industries. In addition, it engages in the distribution of equipment, supplies, and materials; lamination of PCBs; and assembly of laser photoplotters, exposure machines, and other PCB equipment for the PCB industry. The company was founded in 1980 and is based in Singapore.
